text: The saddled moray eel (Gymnothorax conspersus) is a moray eel found in the western Atlantic Ocean.Gymnothorax conspersus at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by Felipe Poey in 1867.Common names for Gymnothorax conspersus at www.fishbase.org. ==References== saddled moray Category:Fauna of the Southeastern United States Category:Fish of the Western Atlantic saddled moray
